rows.label: tlk70000064_01_msg0001
rows.name:
Once, Punpun went to Iiran capital.
But, only once.

rows.label: tlk70000064_01_msg0002
rows.name:
Oh! The Fizzy-busy markets! The
pretty-witty gardens! These things
make impression on Punpun.

rows.label: tlk70000064_01_msg0003
rows.name:
But more than that... Punpun like to see
the happy-happy Drivers, Blades, and
adventurers of Iiran capital.

rows.label: tlk70000064_01_msg0004
rows.name:
Peaceful coexistence much in tune with
pacifist heart-strings of Punpun. Heart
felt like it had found home.
